# 🏆 Sukrut Premier League: Official Auction Guide

Welcome to the **10X Upgrade** of the SPL Auction Portal. This guide contains everything you need to know to access and navigate the mission-critical systems during the live auction.

---

## 🚀 The Portal
**URL**: [https://sukrut-cric.vercel.app](https://sukrut-cric.vercel.app)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The app uses **Real-time Synchronization**. Ensure you have a stable internet connection for the best experience.

---

## 🛡️ For Admins: Tactical Ops Console
The Admin Portal is your mission control. You manage the pulse of the auction.

### 🔑 Access
1. Visit the [Login Page](https://sukrut-cric.vercel.app/login?role=admin).
2. Use the credentials specifically provided for **Intel/Tactical Ops**.
3. **Role Check**: Ensure "Tactical Ops" is displayed at the top.

### 🎮 Features
- **Live Controller**: Use the "SOLD" and "UNSOLD" buttons to finalize bids. 
- **Player Queue**: Deploy the next player to the block with a single click.
- **System Settings**: Control bid increments and auction status (Start/Pause) from the "Economic Protocols" tab.
- **Victory Feedback**: Upon clicking "SOLD", a celebratory confetti effect will trigger globally!

---

## 👨‍✈️ For Captains: Battle Station
Your dashboard is designed for high-stakes decision making.

### 🔑 Access
1. Visit the [Login Page](https://sukrut-cric.vercel.app/login?role=captain).
2. **Email**: `captain[number]@sukrut.com`
3. **Password**: `captain[number]@123`
   *(Example: Captain #1 uses `captain1@sukrut.com` and `captain1@123`)*

### 💥 Bidding Strategy
- **The Bid Button**: A single tap submits the next valid bid. The button pulses when you are "Engaging" (sending bid).
- **Valuation**: Real-time ticker shows the current highest bid and your team's name if you are the lead bidder.
- **Fuel Gauge (Purse)**: Monitor your "Available Purse" carefully. It turns from Gold to Red as your funds deplete.
- **Fleet Combatants (Roster)**: Track your acquired assets in the bottom section. Each player's tier (A+, A, etc.) is highlighted.

> [!TIP]
> **Mission Accomplished!** When you win a player, a full-screen victory overlay will appear. Celebrate, then focus on your next target!

---

## 🛠️ Troubleshooting
- **Lag?**: Refresh the page. The Supabase real-time engine will resync your state immediately.
- **Login Issues?**: Ensure you are on the correct portal (Admin vs. Captain). There is a "Terminal Switch" button at the bottom of the login card.

